{
  "stem": "10181.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They didn't make it to Switzerland because there was some hitch developed in-- in the exchange.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But they weren't sent back to Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They were sent to a different camp near the Swiss border, like a-- internment-- internment camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It wasn't as bad as Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But that was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then the-- the commandant changed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We got Josef Kramer to be the commandant of Bergen-Belsen, and he had been in Auschwitz, OK?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he decided that Bergen-Belsen was a concentration camp, and if-- you know, this is what it's supposed to be, and this is what it's going to be.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the meanwhile, towards the fall of 1944, many more people arrived.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First of all, we got more people coming from Holland.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We got some people from France who came into our camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "From-- Greek, a few more Greeks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nothing which was happening-- I explained to you at the beginning that the Greeks were in charge who from Salonica who had been there before us who received all the food and were corrupt.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and-- and where the-- the-- the Jewish commandant was a Greek, and there were--.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In the summer, in the middle of the summer, the Germans decided that they were too corrupt or whatever.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't know how-- I mean, how they came to that conclusion.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, they were obviously, but they got rid of them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know, they weren't going to allow them to run the camp anymore.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they brought in kapos, you know, kapos from outside, not from within-- non-Jewish, mostly Poles, non-Jewish.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And like I said, and-- to run the camp from within.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I remember the picture of-- there was constant roll call that day when it happened.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was like a revolution, internal revolution.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Nobody knew quite what was happening.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
